dashboardMetadata.name: Business Insights - Home Page Overview (Real Users)

tiles.name: Errors by Origin and Type Per Min
metricExpressions: resolution=null&(builtin:apps.web.action.countOfErrors:filter(and(or(in("dt.entity.application_method",entitySelector("type(application_method),entityName.equals(~"loading of home page~")"))),or(eq("User type","Real users")))):splitBy("Error origin","Error type"):value:rate(1m):setUnit(PerMinute):sort(value(sum,descending)):limit(20)):limit(100):names:fold(auto)

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query:
SELECT COUNT(*), useraction.apdexCategory as "Apdex"
FROM usersession 
 WHERE useraction.application = "www.ulta.com" AND useraction.type = "Load" AND userType="REAL_USER" AND useraction.name = "loading of home page" AND browserType="Desktop Browser"
GROUP BY Apdex

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query:
SELECT DATETIME(starttime, "MM/dd", "1d") AS "Date", Count(*) as "Exit Count"
 FROM useraction WHERE application="www.ulta.com" and apdexCategory in ("TOLERATING", "FRUSTRATED") and (isExitAction=true or usersession.bounce=true) and name = "loading of home page" GROUP BY Date Order By Date

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query:
SELECT usersession.userType as "User Type", Count(*) as Count
 FROM useraction 
 WHERE application="www.ulta.com" and name = "loading of home page"
GROUP BY usersession.userType
ORDER BY Count ASC

tiles.customName: Home Page SI (>2s) Impact on Site Exit
tiles.query:
SELECT isExitAction, Count(*) as "Count"
 FROM useraction WHERE application="www.ulta.com" and speedIndex > 2000 and name = "loading of home page" and usersession.userType="REAL_USER" GROUP BY isExitAction ORDER BY Count
